@node ASMIR "Asmira, Holy Avenger"

@{b}Asmira, Holy Avenger@{ub}

Color   = Green/White
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Summon Legend (2/3)
Cost    = GW2
Artist  = Rebecca Guay

Text(MI): At the end of each turn, put a +1/+1 counter on Asmira, Holy
          Avenger for each creature put into your graveyard from play
          that turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}"Omens lie in this early harvest's fruit."
               -Asmira, Holy Avenger

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node BENTH "Benthic Djinn"

@{b}Benthic Djinn@{ub}

Color   = Black/Blue
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Summon Djinn (5/3)
Cost    = 2BU
Artist  = Adam Rex

Text(MI): Islandwalk.
          During your upkeep, lose 2 life.

Flavor Text: @{i}"In all my years I've only met one mage who successfully
               trapped a djinn-and none who tried and failed."
               -Talibah, embermage

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CADAV "Cadaverous Bloom"

@{b}Cadaverous Bloom@{ub}

Color   = Black/Green
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3BG
Artist  = Alan Rabinowitz

Text(MI): Choose a card in your hand and remove it from the game: Add <BB>
          or <GG> to your mana pool. Play this ability as a mana source.

Flavor Text: @{i}"It's filthy work, planting them."
               -Kifimbo, Shadow Guildmage

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CIRCL "Circle of Despair"

@{b}Circle of Despair@{ub}

Color   = Black/White
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 1BW
Artist  = Scott Fischer

Text(MI): <1>: Sacrifice a creature: Prevent all damage to any creature or
