Flavor Text: @{i}"Life is a resource that should belong only to the strong."
               -Shauku, Endbringer

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node DELIR "Delirium"

@{b}Delirium@{ub}

Color   = Black/Red
Rarity  = MI(U)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = 1BR
Artist  = Terese Nielsen

Text(MI): Play only on target opponent's turn. Tap target creature that
          player controls. That creature deals to the player an amount
          of damage equal to its power. The creature neither deals nor
          receives combat damage this turn.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_D.guide/DELER}

@endnode
@node DISCO "Discordant Spirit"

@{b}Discordant Spirit@{ub}

Color   = Black/Red
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Summon Spirit (2/2)
Cost    = 2BR
Artist  = Alan Rabinowitz

Text(MI): At end of target opponent's turn, put a +1/+1 counter on
          Discordant Spirit for each 1 damage dealt to you this
          turn. At the end of you turn, remove all these counters
          from Discordant Spirit.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_D.guide/DISPI}

@endnode
