@node MALIG "Malignant Growth"

@{b}Malignant Growth@{ub}

Color   = Blue/Green
Rarity  = MI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 3UG
Artist  = Scott Fischer

Text(MI): Cumulative upkeep <1>.
          During your upkeep, put a growth counter on Malignant Growth.
          During target opponent's draw phase, he or she draws an
          additional card for each growth counter on Malignant Growth.
          For each card that opponent draws in this way, Malignant Growth
          deals 1 damage to him or her.

Flavor Text: @{i}No Flavor Text@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_M.guide/MALIG}

